
Cancellation & Refund Policy
At balvant.in, we strive to ensure your satisfaction with our products and services. If you wish to cancel your subscription or request a refund, please review our policy below:

Cancellation
You can cancel your subscription at any time by contacting our support team at contact@balvant.in Please note that cancellation requests must be submitted at least 5 days before your next billing cycle to avoid being charged for the following period.

Refunds
Refund requests are subject to review and approval by our team. We offer refunds for unused portions of prepaid services within 5 days of the initial purchase. Refunds will be processed to the original payment method within 5 days of approval.
